## Commands

- `task dev` — Start development servers
- `task test` — Run test suite
- `task lint` — Lint all code
- `task typecheck` — Type check all code
- `task format` — Auto-format code
- `task db:migrate` — Run database migrations

## Architecture Layers

```text
backend/src/{{ project_slug }}/
├── core/           # Domain (entities, interfaces, value objects) — NO external deps
├── application/    # Use cases (services, DTOs, commands) — depends on core only
├── infrastructure/ # Implementations (DB, cache, APIs) — implements core interfaces
├── presentation/   # Delivery (routes, schemas, CLI) — depends on application
└── composition/    # DI wiring — depends on all
```
